{"tid":1357562,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你地！唔好俾何妖沖淡上環事件！","createTime":"2019-07-23T17:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T19:07:17.000Z","uid":271775,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5490d105c4f3dffd277094b60df97a27864443a","tid":1357562,"uid":271775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:50:43.000Z","msg":"7.21 上環催淚彈直射示威者實錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mzKVjk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mzKVjk.gif&h=707ad722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好俾何妖沖淡上環黑警濫暴！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！缺！一！不！可！<br />\n香港人！不！撤！不！散！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>義士不是condom！<br />\n說好的一個都不能少！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n二、釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n三、撤回612暴動定性<br />\n四、追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n五、立即實行雙普選，還我真香港！</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16xijK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16xijK.png&h=9fb73358&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXaewEN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXaewEN.png&h=6e7eb5c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55672d0fa0c642c80f561d4674bdb5490f1ffd2a","tid":1357562,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"d68e8536977af65189799a5175cf70576d473dc8","tid":1357562,"uid":271775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"55672d0fa0c642c80f561d4674bdb5490f1ffd2a","tid":1357562,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"P"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:54:37.000Z","msg":"P又點唔p又點<br />\n以家focus 返721上環先啦<br />\n個個都focus 曬元朗咁